snippet.title: La La Land 4
snippet.description:
This is La La Land 4, an abstract and enigmatic game made with gamemaker by TheAnemic, A.K.A Biggt. I've been looking for videos of this series of games around all youtube, but never found one, so I decide to play them and record myself.  I dont even know if I have passed the game or not!

Youtube user meowmeow50us also did rip all the music and sprites from all the games, you can download it here:

Sprites- http://www.mediafire.com/file/ucntsg98s87ud3w/La%20La%20Land%20Series%20Sprites.zip

Music- http://www.mediafire.com/file/hfw6xn5b69zbsw8/La%20La%20Land%20Series%20Music.zip
